deals.title: Tandoori Paneer Sandwich
deals.itemDescription: This sandwich begins with a substantial filling of paneer, cheese-like curds marinated in a potent blend of yogurt and classic tandoori spices—smoky paprika, earthy cumin, fragrant coriander, and a hint of fiery chili. The paneer is then charred to perfection, either in a true tandoor or roasted, giving it a smoky depth and a beautifully caramelized exterior.
